    <title>Favor Trader</title>
    <style>
        .fa-big{
            font-size: 300px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-primary">
        <div class="container-fluid">
          <span class="navbar-brand">Favor Trader</span>
            <a class="nav-link text-white" href="#">Login</a>
          </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <main class="container">
        <br>
        <br>
        <h2>What is Favor Trader?</h2>
        <br>
        <p>People are overwhelmed with unfinished tasks within the household, and seeking a trustworthy vendor to fulfill such a task takes time and money.</p>
        <p>Inspired by the barter system, Favor Trader is a platform where talented individuals within a user's zip code can exchange/swap favors for free.</p>
        <p>Each user discloses what they need and what they are offering. The search criteria match based on zip code.</p>
        <p>Everyone loves to save money and time, and since such transactions occur in the real world, why can't they happen online?</p>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
                <ul class="nav nav-tabs">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                      <a class="nav-link active" data-bs-toggle="tab" href="#seek">What I Need</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                      <a class="nav-link" data-bs-toggle="tab" href="#offer">What I Offer</a>
                    </li>
                  
                </ul>
                <div id="myTabContent" class="tab-content my-4">
                    <div class="tab-pane fade active show" id="seek">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Seek someone to dog-sit while on vacation.</li>
                            <li>Seek someone to help mount a TV to the living room wall.</li>
                            <li>Seek someone to pick up your mail.</li>
                            <li>Seek someone to water your plants.</li>
                            <li>Seek someone to move heavy items to the garage.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tab-pane fade" id="offer">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Offer to pick up medicine for a homebound senior.</li>
                            <li>Offer to walk someone's dog.</li>
                            <li>Offer to paint a neighbor's garage.</li>
                            <li>Offer to watch someone's cat.</li>
                            <li>Offer to housesit while a neighbor is on vacation.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
                <div class="row justify-content-center align-items-center">
                    <i class="far fa-handshake fa-big"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </main>
    <!-- JavaScript Bundle with Popper -->
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-MrcW6ZMFYlzcLA8Nl+NtUVF0sA7MsXsP1UyJoMp4YLEuNSfAP+JcXn/tWtIaxVXM" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
